  <h1>Lazy evaluation in Haskell, explained</h1>
  <div class="artmeta"><span>By Coldwast</span><span>Updated Jun 14, 2026</span><span>8 min read</span><span class="tag">#haskell</span><span class="tag">#laziness</span><span class="tag">#concepts</span></div>
  <nav class="toc" id="toc"></nav>
  <figure>
    <img class="hero" src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/2004161/pexels-photo-2004161.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1200" alt="Colourful source code on a screen" width="1200" height="420" loading="eager" />
